  <div class="col-sm-4">
    <h2>How it Works</h2>
    <p>
      We provide users with a simple but powerful markup language called Bamboo to create slide files
      in their github repositories.
    </p>
    <p>
      <ol>
        <li>Create a github repo or clone our example repo</li>
        <li>Use our markup language to create a .gitdeck file in the root of the repo</li>
        <li>Add the repo link to your profile</li>
        <li>We parse your .gitdeck file and generate your slides</li>
        <li>Access them from anywhere using a custom url</li>
      </ol>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-4">
    <h2>Documentation</h2>
